{"tid":2207982,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"dllm 一人一個閪到爆嘅做facial經驗","createTime":"2020-09-18T13:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T23:42:31.000Z","uid":255708,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c30e6b832bdeb4b043274b6dd73b4147ebca429","tid":2207982,"uid":255708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"話説小弟皮膚頗差 想做下facial<br />\n之前去完間係尖沙咀嘅美容院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入到去填完資料要入個啲顧問房<br />\n然之後開始嚟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身諗住做兩個treatments<br />\n點知條女話建議你做另一個treatment(再貴啲)<br />\n話咩呢個你揀嘅treatment唔太啱你做<br />\n但係畢竟第一次去 諗住試下啫<br />\n而且原本諗好要做既 <br />\n佢又話唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就拒絕咗佢嘅建議<br />\n諗住下一次再嚟試<br />\n跟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友塊面即刻黑撚過舊炭咁<br />\n好啦 到做完treatment <br />\n又再sell多次 今次sell啲仲貴嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(做緊facial已經係咁sell)<br />\n狂sell佢地成萬蚊嘅package<br />\n咁撚黑sell梗係唔撚幫襯啦 屌你老母咩<br />\n然之後走個時<br />\n前枱個啲人個個黑住塊面<br />\n棟撚曬係到望住你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似趕客咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">利申:間野係ig好撚出名 <br />\n個撚個YouTuber/KOL都係到介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知再開名 防止大家被人呃<br />\n被錢又要受到啲咁嘅服務態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"5f873f0e678942e3fb1ba8ac97de6c4f18b3888e","tid":2207982,"uid":255708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a33888ff289239dd330918c134da826a77d96c6f","tid":2207982,"uid":255708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:55:3